scene.message:
S.C. President: If I get{nl}
through this, I'll go down{nl}
as a great S.C. president...{waitkey}If you want to help{nl}
the school, go solve{nl}
this incident.{waitkey}{ret}

S.C. President: Old records?{nl}
I sorted those out ages ago.{nl}
What a job that was!{waitkey}What, you want to see{nl}
them?! No way!{nl}
It was a lot of work!{waitkey}Go ask someone who{nl}
knows about{nl}
old stuff!{waitkey}{ret}

Council Member: While we{nl}
run around keeping{nl}
everyone safe,{waitkey}{clearbox}the president just sits{nl}
here doing nothing...{waitkey}{clearbox}He really shouldn't{nl}
have been made{nl}
president!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Student Council President.{nl}
Heads St. Hermelin's{nl}
student council.{nl}
Not very hardworking.{waitkey}{ret}
